title: Alber Seafoods is hiring for all positions, day & night
text:
Alber Seafoods is hiring for all positions, day & night ad date: 10/24/2015 
Alber Seafoods is hiring for all positions, day & night shifts, for the upcoming crab season. Experience w/cooking, quality control, packing, & forklift may qualify for higher wages. Must be able to work in a fast paced environment and conduct yourself in a professional manner. Applications are available at 161 Starfish Way, Crescent City, CA 95531.
